{"tid":2512174,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"請教 三保問題(updated)","createTime":"2021-05-01T13:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T15:41:47.000Z","uid":76740,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"39aa022fd4cf3ca45ac47beacc773fb478742361","tid":2512174,"uid":76740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:03:16.000Z","msg":"請教 三保問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2421563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2421563</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n推唔到舊post上來所以開過個新post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n差唔多三個月前我揸電單車自炒<br />\n<br />\n隔離線私家車驚碌到我 都搞到自炒<br />\n<br />\n警方果邊就調查完 話冇足夠證據檢控我/對方<br />\n<br />\n姐係唔會告我 不小心駕駛<br />\n<br />\n咁呢個情況 對方如果民事索償我 我份保險係<br />\n<br />\n咪都會包?<br />\n<br />\n另外想問下 有冇巴打知 呢個情況下<br />\n<br />\n對家會唔會最後都追究唔到我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 姐係佢成功民事索償我嘅機會大唔大<br />\n<br />\n因為警方果邊調查完 都冇指控我<br />\n<br />\n咁可能唔關我事?"},{"pid":"0bb601374f556e8790de1d2bb61729c4f80f5d09","tid":2512174,"uid":76740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:04:16.000Z","msg":"*註 隔離線私家車 唔係我後車 所以冇話要留2秒距離"},{"pid":"d001a33d6bfc6c36ee4d91234ceb3e6498192f07","tid":2512174,"uid":76740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:13:22.000Z","msg":"同埋我開頭唔識 有喺wtsapp到承認責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咪玩完"},{"pid":"2d0934fca99fb250e51e22ce2f141305b20011c0","tid":2512174,"uid":215175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T15:41:47.000Z","msg":"當時有冇報保險？<br />\n如果有，保險會處"}]}